{"tid":2170320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳木勝鼻咽癌離世","createTime":"2020-08-23T07:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T08:17:21.000Z","uid":129741,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d2264fc1cccd0692360bf4aeac7fd41fc39d06ff","tid":2170320,"uid":129741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:38:33.000Z","msg":"香港導演陳木勝今早不幸因鼻咽癌離世，終年58歲，遺下太太及3子女，而其遺孀心情非常悲傷，至今仍未平服。他最後一部作品是執導由甄子丹和謝霆鋒主演的《怒火》，影片於去年底已拍竣，正待排期上映。據知，他於拍攝電影期間已感身體不適，之後去做了身體檢查，不幸驗出已患上鼻咽癌末期，到拍攝完成已無能力做後期，需交由其他人接手工作。"},{"pid":"a291c2639e2bee185a3b23ddd78990192cfb9d53","tid":2170320,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:39:05.000Z","msg":"可惜"},{"pid":"fc5a8da6ba3d595387bed1753f90563bb274d6aa","tid":2170320,"uid":1837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:40:23.000Z","msg":"咁後生一黎就末期"},{"pid":"432281584d50426149795148a02b7a7b1840428e","tid":2170320,"uid":272565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"a499a21a131ccf03bb0abe1b1304e43ff41be923","tid":2170320,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:54:50.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"280632431788a828526d94055945005c40f7f4ea","tid":2170320,"uid":165536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc5a8da6ba3d595387bed1753f90563bb274d6aa","tid":2170320,"uid":1837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:40:23.000Z","msg":"咁後生一黎就末期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:15:46.000Z","msg":"鼻咽癌通常發現都至少第三期"},{"pid":"debed85bb8c04029cdac5a3f14a3fb6f0abd9dfb","tid":2170320,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}